'''[[Efavan/Legends|Efavan]] Port''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] located in the city Efavan, which was the capital of [[Vorzyd V/Legends|Vorzyd V]]. [[The Port Line]] passenger conveyor tube connected the port with the casinos in the city's [[Westrex]] district.

